# Chemical diagram formulas(SMILES)
Chemical formulas can be represented using SMILES syntax.

SMILES formulas can be rendered inline via <smiles>OC(=O)c1cc(Cl)cs1</smiles> or block mode via:
```smiles
OC(=O)c1cc(Cl)cs1
```

